{"type":null,"faqId":44813,"title":"为什么屏幕突然缩小，并偏在左下角或右下角？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">为了便于您单手操作手机，系统提供了单手屏幕功能。在手机屏幕底部的虚拟键栏位置，向左平移，桌面向左缩小；向右平移，桌面向右缩小。反向滑动则可以恢复正常大小。如果不需要，可以关闭此功能：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">“设置 &gt; 全部设置 &gt; 智能辅助 &gt; 单手操作 &gt; 单手屏幕”。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"314","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409266000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":6,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"单手屏幕","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}